there are 3 types of people looking to get hired at crypto startups:
1) crypto-native
2) crypto-pilled
3) crypto-curious

Look for 1s and 2s. A good 2 can learn incredibly fast and become a 1 in no time. 

Beware of 3s. They rarely have enough drive + passion to go deep enough.
